sentences.sentence: A method was developed to determine atrazine and acetochlor in water.
sentences.translation: 本文确立了水中莠去津、乙草胺残留量检测方法。

sentences.sentence: A new dispersing agent (WPJ - a) for 38% atrazine suspension concentrates was developed.
sentences.translation: 研制了用于38%莠去津悬浮剂的新型分散剂(WPJ - A)。

sentences.sentence: Recent review of current progress of study on microorganisms degradation and transforming into atrazine was presented abroad.
sentences.translation: 综述了近年来国外微生物降解转化阿特拉津的新研究进展。
